  <Summary>With Battlestone apparently dead, Brigade tries to pick up the pieces and carry on without their esteemed leader. The team confronts Thermal about the expose she wrote about them which caused the current crisis in the first place. Thermal searches through Battlestone's personal effects and discovers that he was her half-brother. Seahawk steps up to lead Brigade but immediately starts an all out brawl with his brother, Coldsnap. Crypt arrives to make a bad situation even worse.</Summary>
